data.description: Come check out this great Investment property, 2 unit Multi Family Home down in Dayton KY. Unit one is a 1 Bed 1 Bath thats been recently painted, new Kitchen Appliances, bathroom renovated, and all new ceiling fans. This unit rents for 1200 a month and tenants lease is up 4-6-24. Unit 2 is upstairs and is a 2 Bed 1 Bath, that has been recently painted, and new Kitchen Appliances. It is currently being rented for 1250 a month and lease is up 3-31-24.  Multi Family home also has a two car garge and driveway in back!
